59.6	Justin_Hall	Justin Hall	Justin Hall (born December 16, 1974 in Chicago, Illinois), is an American freelance journalist who is best known as a pioneer blogger (internet-based diarist), and for writing reviews from game conferences such as E3 as well as the Tokyo Game Show.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/JustinHallJoiIto.jpg/220px-JustinHallJoiIto.jpg
